{"tid":234884,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"熱刺球員集體中毒輸波","createTime":"2017-05-08T15:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T21:17:14.000Z","uid":41515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1af8e9562a6a752c1f1603a832050efb76e3cfb","tid":234884,"uid":41515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:04:19.000Z","msg":"英格蘭超級聯賽球隊熱刺（ Tottenham Hotspur）前日煞科戰中，2比1敗給韋斯咸，更緣慳下季歐洲聯賽冠軍盃。一場敗戰，背後原來大有文章，事緣熱刺球員於煞科戰前一晚，於酒店食自助餐集體食物中毒，10名主力球員，包括隊長羅比堅尼全部屙嘔致腳軟，球員帶病死撐上場，結果落敗。球會揚言要控告涉案酒店，索償1,000萬鎊（約1億4,400多萬港元）。<br />\n認真當黑的熱刺，上周六在倫敦萬豪（ Marriott Hotel）食賽前自助大餐，豈料到周日早上，球員陸續病倒。領隊祖爾隨即報警，球會亦跟英超聯方面申請押後比賽，或延遲至當日下午6時，但英超聯指熱刺有足夠替補，拒絕押後比賽，球員惟有帶病上陣。英國《太陽報》更指酒店內1名廚房工人，是熱刺死敵阿仙奴球迷，有最大嫌疑。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20060509/5904075\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20060509%2F5904075&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=521e84ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20060509%2F5904075&h=51535c02\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20060509/5904075</a>"},{"pid":"08c152110f38b63950ce0aad5571fe8c2c35eee0","tid":234884,"uid":36142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ac1b246a725b4cd679cc66e62355d9d8124e14","tid":234884,"uid":58375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://arsenalgalaxy.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/chef-wenger.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Farsenalgalaxy.files.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F01%2Fchef-wenger.jpg&h=e900c8db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbd75e4ab30a14cc25c40b045c1889f089494dc3","tid":234884,"uid":93874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:25:30.000Z","msg":"屌 堅唔堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/no